<div style="width:0;height:0;clear:both"></div><dl class="lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle-">
<dd class="lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle-title">
<h1>夜叉王</h1>
<h2>（漫画《圣传》人物）</h2>
<a class="edit-lemma cmn-btn-hover-blue cmn-btn-28 j-edit-link" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
<a class="lock-lemma" href="javascript:;" nslog-type="10003105" target="_blank" title="锁定"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_lock-lemma"></em>锁定</a>
<a class="lemma-discussion cmn-btn-hover-blue cmn-btn-28 j-discussion-link" href="/planet/talk?lemmaId=1445299" nslog-type="90000102" target="_blank"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_discussion-solid"></em>讨论<span class="num">999</span></a>
</dd>
</dl><div class="promotion-declaration">
</div><div class="lemma-summary" label-module="lemmaSummary">
<div class="para" label-module="para">夜叉王出自漫画《<a data-lemmaid="22486" href="/item/%E5%9C%A3%E4%BC%A0/22486" target="_blank">圣传</a>》。夜叉族年轻的领导人，也是夜摩刀的主人。天界的万人迷大帅哥，身负率领族人同魔族战斗捍卫天界北方边境的职责。</div><div class="para" label-module="para">夜叉王是个希腊式悲剧英雄，为救阿修罗全族被诛，但又背负着被阿修罗杀死的预言。</div>
</div>
<div class="configModuleBanner">
</div><div class="basic-info cmn-clearfix">
<dl class="basicInfo-block basicInfo-left">
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">中文名</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
夜叉王
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">配    音</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
<a href="/item/%E9%80%9F%E6%B0%B4%E5%A5%96" target="_blank">速水奖</a>
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">登场作品</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
《<a data-lemmaid="22486" href="/item/%E5%9C%A3%E4%BC%A0/22486" target="_blank">圣传</a>》
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">性    别</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
男
</dd>
</dl><dl class="basicInfo-block basicInfo-right">
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">身    份</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
“六星”之一
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">武    器</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
夜摩刀
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">族    别</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
夜叉族
</dd>
