<div class="anchor-list">
<a class="lemma-anchor para-title" name="1"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="sub19093299_1"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="角色原型"></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">夜叉王</span>角色原型</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="1" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">《圣传》的人物原型源自古印度神话《梨俱吠陀》和大乘佛教经典中常说的天龙八部。<a data-lemmaid="5446" href="/item/%E5%A4%A9%E9%BE%99%E5%85%AB%E9%83%A8/5446" target="_blank">天龙八部</a>（八部众）：<a href="/item/%E5%A4%A9%E4%BC%97" target="_blank">天众</a>、<a href="/item/%E9%BE%99%E4%BC%97" target="_blank">龙众</a>、<a href="/item/%E5%A4%9C%E5%8F%89" target="_blank">夜叉</a>、<a href="/item/%E9%98%BF%E4%BF%AE%E7%BD%97" target="_blank">阿修罗</a>、<a href="/item/%E8%BF%A6%E6%A5%BC%E7%BD%97" target="_blank">迦楼罗</a>、<a href="/item/%E5%B9%B2%E9%97%BC%E5%A9%86" target="_blank">干闼婆</a>、<a href="/item/%E7%B4%A7%E9%82%A3%E7%BD%97" target="_blank">紧那罗</a>、<a href="/item/%E6%91%A9%E5%91%BC%E7%BD%97%E8%BF%A6" target="_blank">摩呼罗迦</a>八类佛教的护法。</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a class="lemma-anchor para-title" name="2"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="sub19093299_2"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="角色经历"></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">夜叉王</span>角色经历</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="2" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">为了挽救阿修罗而背叛帝释天，全族被诛。从此，他顺从命运成为六星，为成为灭天之破而走上流浪生涯。深爱阿修罗的同时，他又背负着将被阿修罗杀死的预言，是一个长着棺材脸的希腊式悲剧英雄。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"></div>
<div class="anchor-list">
<a class="lemma-anchor a" name="a"></a>
